\"font-size: xx-large;\">立會過半，狗糧減半<br />\n全民派錢，永不落空</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9月參選人立刻發動及宣傳政綱,削減驚方預算,慳返果D錢派比市民<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fdtdPS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fdtdPS</a><br />\n<br />\n既然777無恥派錢,<br />\n我地都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,<br />\n<br />\n依家即刻宣傳政綱,<br />\n9月立會一過半,<br />\n就即刻發動議案,<br />\n削減驚方預算，<br />\n<br />\n驚方1年預算258億元,<br />\n削減一半就130億元,<br />\n4年立法任期就520億元,<br />\n再叫政府比D錢來,<br />\n就儲夠710億,<br />\n下年又可以派一萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a44c4620d03d01c4cc6de9d694f41c0e24e0adb","tid":1900870,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7102d58d90f1ad117b3ee458e7e479fe701cd598","tid":1900870,"uid":40682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}